
Shateki - Knockdown Game
Shateki is a fun, interactive shooting game where players knock items off a shelf to score points. The game features a countdown timer and a leaderboard to track the best scores. Players can submit their scores to the global leaderboard and even share their achievements on Reddit.

Features
Shoot items off the shelf to earn points.

60-second timer to finish the game.

Leaderboard to track global scores.

Reddit integration to share scores.

Username input and validation.

Tech Stack
Frontend: React, React Router, Vite, Framer Motion

Backend: Express, MongoDB

Deployment: Vercel

APIs: Custom API for leaderboard and score submission

CORS: For handling cross-origin requests

